description: Brown-skinned, muscular Jason Vario couldn’t wait to get home so he could finally get some shut eye, but to his dismay slender, athletic Kit Cohen and beefy, blond-haired William Seed were in the other room making way too much noise. After pleading with them to keep it quiet, and being ignored, he busts through the wall! William and Kit apologetically get down on their knees as they worship his massive, uncut, hung cock, and turn their duo into a trio!
title: Screamers Part 1
